    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s been well-loved, kept clean, and still has so much life left in it! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for your next road trip or daily commute, this is the one. Feel free to reach out\u2014I\u2019d love for you to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
